title: Coleophora albilineella
text: Coleophora albilineella is a <a href="moth">moth</a> of the family <a href="Coleophoridae">Coleophoridae</a>. It is found in <a href="Spain">Spain</a>, <a href="France">France</a>, <a href="Sardinia">Sardinia</a>, <a href="Austria">Austria</a>, the <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>, <a href="Slovakia">Slovakia</a>, <a href="Hungary">Hungary</a>, <a href="Romania">Romania</a>, <a href="Greece">Greece</a> and southern <a href="Russia">Russia</a>.
